    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>石器时代的殖民地模拟</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/d47e5456dc33a5b5a3c0513eb958acab.poster.avif?t=1767527078\" width=800 height=577 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/d47e5456dc33a5b5a3c0513eb958acab.webm?t=1767527078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在石器时代建立您自己的定居点并建造一个繁荣的殖民地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领您的定居者探索新土地，收集资源，建造建筑，创建一个安全且自给自足的村庄。您的战略选择将决定定居点的生存和繁荣，使您的部落逐渐扩展并成长为一个强大的殖民地。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/f8f4afb9f6d40beaf2783b7a28a6625c.poster.avif?t=1767527078\" width=800 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/f8f4afb9f6d40beaf2783b7a28a6625c.webm?t=1767527078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有欲望和意志的定居者</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/f701be89796654a65faccb62ca786de0.poster.avif?t=1767527078\" width=800 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/f701be89796654a65faccb62ca786de0.webm?t=1767527078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定居者饿了会吃饭，累了会睡觉，生病时需要治疗。他们按照自己的欲望行事，但当您为他们分配任务时，他们会勤奋工作，学习必要的技能并在角色中成长。随着定居者的发展，他们会开始渴望更舒适的房屋和更美味的食物。如果这些欲望得不到满足，他们的情绪可能会恶化，有时甚至会导致犯罪或离开部落。他们很简单，但他们信任您，并相信只要遵循您的指示，仓库里就会有食物，舒适的家中也会有他们的休息之地。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用点击管理世界</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/61a0cfa2ece76caae4ee64c7ff183099.poster.avif?t=1767527078\" width=800 height=530 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/61a0cfa2ece76caae4ee64c7ff183099.webm?t=1767527078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过简单的点击和拖动来高效管理您的殖民地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像战略游戏中的单位一样指挥定居者，像管理操作系统中的文件和文件夹一样轻松管理殖民地的资源和建筑。即使没有定居者的帮助，您也可以直接收集资源，移动物品并顺利完成所需任务。以最简单有效的方式管理屏幕之外的殖民地。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过研究建设文明</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/99c2ad4731af9c8ec0af16e46aea2e4b.poster.avif?t=1767527078\" width=800 height=535 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/99c2ad4731af9c8ec0af16e46aea2e4b.webm?t=1767527078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定居者向您献上贡品，渴望获得新知识的启示。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过研究传授智慧，推动定居点的发展。从加工原材料和农业到烘焙等富饶技术，再到防御设施、铁制武器和护甲等安全技术，发展必需的建筑并创造出适应更强大、更多样化环境的殖民地。通过您的智慧，定居者将成长并与您共同实现更多成就。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/9e99bbb13bfbfffebcf372d3d8694dee.poster.avif?t=1767527078\" width=800 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/9e99bbb13bfbfffebcf372d3d8694dee.webm?t=1767527078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理定居者，发展殖民地</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/e2aaeb6a15bd31002d8fd142d48ce33a.poster.avif?t=1767527078\" width=800 height=530 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259660/extras/e2aaeb6a15bd31002d8fd142d48ce33a.webm?t=1767527078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有效管理定居者，以推动殖民地的发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为定居者装备护甲和武器，将他们变成士兵，加强殖民地的防御，或提供工具支持他们高效工作。此外，可以通过再教育接纳野蛮人成为新的忠实定居者，或将他们囚禁以获得神圣的力量。随着时间推移，您的追随者增加，您可以应对食物短缺、犯罪和社会问题，引导定居点朝着您想要的方向发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
